examples.en: He blew heavily through his nostrils.
His nostrils were flaring with anger.
A terrible stench saluted our nostrils.
examples.ru: Жуткая вонь ударила нам в ноздри.

examples.en: She left in a rage, her nostrils flaring.
The smell of gunpowder filled his nostrils.
The smell of rotten meat assailed her nostrils.
examples.ru: Запах гнилого мяса ударил ей в ноздри.
